cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.IT 

This paper is about mobile edge caching, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and wireless communication. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also proposes an online learning algorithm, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely category as well. Additionally, the algorithm uses linear models and perturbations, which are related to mathematical optimization and control theory, respectively, making cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) possible categories. Finally, the paper deals with content popularity and caching decisions, which are related to information theory, making cs.IT (Information Theory) a possible category as well.
